These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: disaster, musical, romance, sports, superhero
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk, milk, tea, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
6. the person watching disaster movies is in the middle##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | romance | disaster | superhero | sports |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | fanta | milk     | tea       | soy-milk  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
5 different pets are kept: dog, pony, fish, horse, chinchilla
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: disco, indie, metal, r&b, rock
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the left of the fan of indie##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
4. the owner of the dog is in the middle##1
5. the owner of the pony is the fan of metal##1
6. the fan of rock is the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Pet      | pony | fish | dog | horse | chinchilla |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | r&b   | disco       | indie    | rock   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skateboarding, rugby, cycling, cricket, soccer
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, bus, jet-ski, ship, subway
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Sport        | cycling | cricket | rugby | skateboarding | soccer |
| Transport   | bus  | boat      | subway | jet-ski | ship      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, fishing, reading, sudoku, traveling
City: berlin, boston, san-francisco, liverpool, rome
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1
7. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Hobby   | sudoku    | baking        | reading | fishing | traveling |
| City     | berlin | liverpool | rome  | boston   | san-francisco |

