.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
There 5 different types of food: banana, cherry, grapes, mango, strawberry
5 different pets are kept: cat, rabbit, horse, lizard, snake
1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is the person eating strawberry##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating banana##1
6. the owner of the snake is the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Food    | grapes   | banana     | cherry   | mango         | strawberry |
| Pet   | cat | lizard | horse | snake | rabbit     |

