.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, cricket, handball, volleyball
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, nigerian, colombian, egyptian, brazilian
1. the egyptian is in the middle##1
2. the argentine is on the far right##1
3. the colombian is on the left of the egyptian##1
4. the colombian is the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the brazilian is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Sport       | handball   | cricket   | baseball | volleyball | badminton |
| Nationality   | nigerian | colombian | egyptian   | brazilian | argentine       |

