.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
There are 5 different nationalities: indonesian, australian, polish, russian, spanish
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, biathlon, rugby, tennis, water-polo
1. the polish is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is the indonesian##1
3. the spanish is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the indonesian is on the left of the russian##1
5. the person who's sport is biathlon is in the middle##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Nationality     | australian   | polish  | spanish      | indonesian | russian     |
| Sport   | tennis | rugby | biathlon | baseball   | water-polo |

