.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  chef, engineer, manager, scientist, teacher
There are 5 different nationalities: nigerian, japanese, dutch, french, malaysian
1. the malaysian is on the left of the teacher##1
2. the japanese is on the right of the dutch##1
3. the malaysian is on the right of the french##1
4. the teacher is on the left of the japanese##1
5. the japanese is on the right of the dutch##1
6. the chef is on the right of the engineer##1
7. the nigerian is on the right of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Job     | engineer | chef       | teacher | scientist | manager    |
| Nationality   | french   | malaysian | dutch  | japanese     | nigerian |

