.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-10::.
There are 5 different nationalities: american, argentine, british, italian, nigerian
There 5 different types of food: cranberry, pomegranate, papaya, broccoli, artichoke
1. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the british##1
3. the person eating papaya is the american##1
4. the italian is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
5. the person eating broccoli is in the middle##1
6. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
| Nationality   | nigerian | italian | argentine | british | american |
| Food           | artichoke      | pomegranate    | broccoli  | cranberry     | papaya     |

