.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-11::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: aquamarine, emerald, mauve, lilac, chestnut
5 different pets are kept: cat, dog, goat, rabbit, snake
1. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the dog is the person who likes lilac##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is on the far right##1
6. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
7. the owner of the snake is the person who likes mauve##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |      5      |
| Color   | lilac | aquamarine  | mauve | emerald | chestnut |
| Pet    | dog    | rabbit | snake   | cat       | goat        |

