.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-12::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, baking, drawing, puzzles, writing
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: biathlon, cricket, lacrosse, surfing, weightlifting
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Hobby    | card-games | puzzles          | drawing    | writing | baking  |
| Sport   | lacrosse  | weightlifting | biathlon | surfing | cricket |

