.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
There 5 different types of food: papaya, nectarine, zucchini, pepper, potato
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile, subway, train, tram
1. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is the person eating papaya##1
4. the person eating potato is the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the train is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
6. the person eating pepper is in the middle##1
7. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Food   | zucchini | papaya      | pepper | nectarine | potato |
| Transport     | train  | snowmobile | bus     | tram     | subway  |

