4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the argentine##1
6. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Flower      | marigold | daisy | rose      | azalea | dahlia      |
| Nationality   | dutch  | mexican       | argentine | turkish  | indonesian |

