4. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
6. the person watching romance movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |      5      |
| Food    | asparagus   | blueberry | peach      | apricot | lime        |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | time-travel     | romance | adventure | western |

