4. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person driving the ship is in the middle##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is the person driving the scooter##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |  3   |    4    |   5    |
