.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, milk, mirinda, tea
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: mystery, action, crime, martial-arts, time-travel
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching crime movies is the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
7. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage   | tea     | milk       | 7up     | fanta  | mirinda  |
| Movie-Genre      | martial-arts | mystery | action | time-travel | crime |

